---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionHeader from '../../components/SectionHeader.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Newsletter intelligence | ForgeCore" description="How the ForgeCore publication functions as a live module inside the autonomous revenue system.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="reading">
      <SectionHeader eyebrow="Module" title="Newsletter intelligence" description="A live ForgeCore module that turns research into attention, audience, artifacts, and monetizable distribution." />
      <div class="prose">
        <h3>What it is</h3>
        <p>The publication engine transforms selected signals into issues, archive pages, list growth, and reusable research assets.</p>
        <h3>Why it matters</h3>
        <p>It creates public proof, builds distribution, validates topics, and generates inputs for future products, tools, and offers.</p>
        <h3>Current stack</h3>
        <p>Static render pipeline, Cloudflare Pages deployment, Beehiiv signup, structured research input, and issue publishing.</p>
        <h3>Inputs</h3>
        <p>Research briefs, market signals, editorial filtering, and disciplined topic selection.</p>
        <h3>Outputs</h3>
        <p>Issues, archive pages, subscriber growth, topic validation, and a growing artifact trail.</p>
        <h3>CTA</h3>
        <p><a href="https://news.forgecore.co/">Subscribe to the live module</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
